| DAMAGE color package v1.0
| Set @var msg+your message- then call the color function

@addfunc+
@print,var+
     +[31m(msg)[0m-
@-
@addfunc:createname"red"
@---

@addfunc+
@print,var+
     +[32m(msg)[0m-
@-
@addfunc:createname"green"
@---

@addfunc+
@print,var+
     +[33m(msg)[0m-
@-
@addfunc:createname"yellow"
@---

@addfunc+
@print,var+
     +[34m(msg)[0m-
@-
@addfunc:createname"blue"
@---

@addfunc+
@print+
     +[0m-
@-
@addfunc:createname"reset"
@---
